{"tid":1806691,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「推到民陣見倒」下次遊行主題 2020真雙普選","createTime":"2020-01-01T12:21:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T01:55:39.000Z","uid":217430,"like":65,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"b58761178a843b923a9cc15d6bee3ad638edd5b7","tid":1806691,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T12:21:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">下次遊行主題：<br />\n廢除功能組別 <br />\n2020真雙普選</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n各位同路人，重記唔記得七。一當日點解要攻入立法會嗎？？懇請大家花幾分鐘睇一睇條片。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">七。一立法會宣言</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/SsoKwEDytWE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FSsoKwEDytWE&d=EyvET%2B%2BaCRTqAKFB3QLIcxPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=bee6a1b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/SsoKwEDytWE</a> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解6。9一百萬人大遊行當晚，政府會當香港人係臭四，如期二讀。<br />\n點解呢半年會有噤多手足被自殺，數千人被濫捕。<br />\n點解警權會無限放大。<br />\n點撚解柒婆、行會同成班高官對呢個殘局完全無需負上任何責任。<br />\n<br />\n大家知唔知點解？講都講撚到口臭。<br />\n問題係個制度。<br />\n<br />\n香港既特首並非普選而來，非民選既特首，洗撚向市民交代。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而立法會亦非全面直選，功能組別呢個怪胎令到立法會應有功能完全失效。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一條「送中」惡法，搞撚到天怒人怨，相信大部分香港人都有強烈既無力感。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而香港人權與民主法案終於係今年11月27日正式生效。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未過條act之前，大家都好撚緊張。不停做文宣，舉行造勢集會。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XZtfo8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXZtfo8o.jpg&h=51da59f4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NpPyaOo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNpPyaOo.jpg&h=eab94dd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n條act生效左一個月了，攬炒巴、學界團隊們為制裁而制作既清算薄並進行得如火如荼了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係、但係真雙普選呢個訴求呢？條act已經講到明支持香港要<span style=\"color: red;\">2020</span>年有真雙普選。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iX9RGVf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiX9RGVf.png&h=9bd9cdda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.congress.gov/bill/116th-congress/senate-bill/1838\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.congress.gov%2Fbill%2F116th-congress%2Fsenate-bill%2F1838&d=EyvET%2B%2BaCRTqAKFB3QLIcxPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=0ab9472c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.congress.gov/bill/116th-congress/senate-bill/1838</a><br />\n<br />\n(5) to support the establishment of a genuine democratic option to freely and fairly nominate and elect the Chief Execu- tive of Hong Kong, and the establishment by <span style=\"color: red;\">2020</span> of open and direct democratic elections for all members of the Hong Kong Legislative Council; <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拍掌得一隻手又點會響....<br />\n老美撐香港2020年要有雙普選，香港人要比反應交戲嫁！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n五大訴求中最重要既永遠都係真雙普選。<br />\n而唔撚係乜野爭奪功能組別議席，唔撚係區選。<br />\n成立公會真正目的並係為左三罷。<br />\n<br />\n我知大家睇到呢度，實有人會屌柒我：「屌你老味，知唔知道乜野叫兩手準備。」「你都onL9, 今日都已經係2020年啦！懵撚！」「白痴！美國佬彩你都有味！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我只知道：</span><br />\n萬惡根源就係制度問題。<br />\n雙普選文宣嚴重不足。<br />\n兩手準備？？定係妹仔大過主人婆？？<br />\n當全世界都搶薑功能組別既時候，五大訴求已經失焦。<br />\n<br />\n唔係2020年真普選，噤等到幾時？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等到2024年？等手足坐夠十年先？？<br />\n定等齊國歌法、二十三條、智慧燈柱呢d撚屌野通過曬先搞雙普選？？<br />\n定等到2047年，自動收皮？？<br />\n<br />\n無時間了各位。我地香港人只有最後一次贏得雙普選的機會。這是一場end game，唔撚係有險可守。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />時間正在倒數：餘下<span style=\"color: red;\">365</span>日。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PD46vOV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPD46vOV.gif&h=d8964a5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n覺得我講既講啱聽既，日後遊行集會多叫幾聲<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「2020，真雙普選」、<br />\n「廢除功能組別，2020真雙普選」<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n覺得我講既野唔啱聽既，可以屌柒我。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我有一個卑微既請求，請大家睇一睇「七一宣言」、回想一下邊班人令「送中」條例成功撒回。<br />\n<br />\n最後都係個幾句：<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span>"},{"pid":"fddb1b63b2274174bb26a3a545ea249864d17b86","tid":1806691,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T12:21:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7b210f80e356dbacc4f5e07c8f7e4654aaa75d0c","tid":1806691,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T12:21:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6e11961e8127f035acb2c08a1441229785002183","tid":1806691,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T12:21:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d233e61d63db780805b00f84e3b0287bca545866","tid":1806691,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T12:23:08.000Z","msg":"民陣快d睇倒"},{"pid":"c7295bda60d381dd69b4c15a3affc1a65986a0c5","tid":1806691,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T12:23:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce327e6ea9912e74bbfdbcf82ee8131deb39cb2c","tid":1806691,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T12:24:29.000Z","msg":"幫手推啦 唔好只係比正評"},{"pid":"784510a71f104ae626b2bb84d59e086268fe999b","tid":1806691,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T12:25:42.000Z","msg":"講白啲就係清除基本法中共控制香港政府嘅權力"},{"pid":"aad982f7160907f6aad6f2b16d25fc661db4a99b","tid":1806691,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T12:25:45.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"